reviewText: The video was ok I guess...... I found the video lacking and how it was produced was kind of lacking . It reminds me of a high school news team. I was thinking it would have got a litter deeper then what it did the flash backs to interviews with the same person was lame. If you watch it more then once you will notice that one person he is interviewing does not want to be doing it .I am glad I did not pay more then $8.00 for the video shipped. If you pay more then $5.00  you wasting your money..
